	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Ok, let me explain how you earn platinum (pp) on this board right now.<br />
<br />
<img src="/forums/images/orangestar.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Register as a member:</b> <font color="orange">100pp</font><br />
<img src="/forums/images/orangestar.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Starting a new thread:</b> <font color="orange">10pp</font><br />
<img src="/forums/images/orangestar.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Making a reply:</b> <font color="orange">5pp</font><br />
<img src="/forums/images/orangestar.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Voting on a poll:</b> <font color="orange">10pp</font><br />
<img src="/forums/images/orangestar.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Owning a thread that get's X replies according to below:</b><font size="1"><ul><li><b>More than 5 replies:</b> <font color="orange">10pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 10 replies:</b> <font color="orange">25pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 20 replies:</b> <font color="orange">75pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 30 replies:</b> <font color="orange">150pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 50 replies:</b> <font color="orange">250pp</font><br />
</ul></font><img src="/forums/images/orangestar.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Owning a thread that get's X views according to below:</b><font size="1"><ul><li><b>More than 10 view:</b> <font color="orange">5pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 50 views:</b> <font color="orange">25pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 100 views:</b> <font color="orange">50pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 200 views:</b> <font color="orange">150pp</font><br />
<li><b>More than 1000 views:</b> <font color="orange">250pp</font><br />
</ul></font><br />
Now keep in mind that this Store system is very much an untested feature that just went live, so we might be adjusting this feature at any time, adding new actions to buy or removing some. We already removed the option to change your username since we couldn't come up with a valid reason anybody would actually spend 5000pp doing it.<br />
<br />
We're also planning to give donators pp to their account for the obvious reason. We're thinking of doing this somewhat based on donation to make it fair. Some sites use different graphics to represent donators of different amount values, but we're as appreciative of $5 as we are when we get $30+ so we don't want to discriminate between users by giving out different graphics. <br />
<br />
However we can easily make a level system for donations within different brackets and give out pp based on that, so that's in the works.<br />
<br />
Hope this clears things up a bit. And as 'someone' found out earlier; there are already several perks to buy in the store right now.<br />
<br />
Question is. Would you guys want a spend link on your posts in the message board, or is it easy enough to track back to the forum index?<br />
<br />
* <b>Remember:</b> Keep checking this post for an updated list of incentives. Don't be shy to test the new "Rate" graphic on posts.</font></p>
	
