	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">I dissapprove the post about the Tax...I also reccommend you dont make it so that you lose pp anymore from negative posts and increase the reward for helpful posts. Also change it to "Did you find this post helpful" for example: In the plas priest robe thread...Guy asked a question, I answered, if he found my answer helpful he'd rate my post, maybe 4 answers "not at all", "A little...I guess" "pretty helpful" "I love you" in terms of helpfulness. Maybe ranging from nothing for "a little...I guess" to 15pp for a "i love you" helpfulness?<br />
<br />
Ok Good, you cant approve your own posts and give yourself pp.<br />
<br />
I think I've found a little bug. I went from 190ish to 340pp in the matter of one click....I'm thinking that the views thing is a little...broked. I'm guessing it compounds previous rewards into the reward for your topics new count...</font></p>
	
